        pricing_overview: '<p>ResearchRabbit executes a massively compelling, aggressive mission-driven pricing structure: it is completely Free for researchers. They explicitly mandate zero paywalls for the core visual discovery features, relying on funding and strategic partnerships to ensure that scientists globally are not economically restricted from advancing human knowledge.</p>',
        comparison_summary: '<p>ResearchRabbit operates in the highly elite "Academic Discovery" sector, competing directly against Connected Papers and traditional titans like Google Scholar. Connected Papers operates similarly by building single-paper visual graphs. ResearchRabbit differentiates itself as the *Massive Algorithmic Ecosystem*. It doesn\'t just build a graph for one paper; it allows users to build massive, synchronized collections, track authors, and receive active AI recommendations, making it the supreme centralized planning engine for a multi-year academic thesis.</p>'
