        pricing_overview: '<p>Retool operates a highly aggressive, classic B2B "Seat-Based" SaaS model. The Free or "Team" tiers act as an excellent playground for startups. However, the exact moment a company requires critical enterprise features—like hosting the platform On-Premise for absolute security, advanced Role-Based Access Control (so the intern cannot accidentally click a button that drops the production database), or custom SSO—they are forced into colossal Enterprise Contracts.</p>',
