        pricing_overview: '<p>Rows executes a highly intelligent, frictionless B2B/B2C SaaS adoption funnel. A highly capable "Free Forever" tier allows users to build infinite spreadsheets with basic native integrations, ensuring viral adoption. The monetization engine lies in the "Plus" and "Pro" tiers, which strictly pay-wall the massive computational limits of the AI integrations (running 100,000 AI cell tasks) and the highest-tier Enterprise API pipeline integrations.</p>',
